      <title>印度利率制定者指望健康增长来降低通胀</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/india-rate-setters-counting-on-healthy-growth-to-lower-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五货币政策会议纪要显示，强劲的增长使得印度的利率制定者能够在更长的时间内维持较高的利率，以确保通胀得到持久降低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/india-rate-setters-counting-on-healthy-growth-to-lower-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:39:46 GMT</pubDate>
