      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尽管物价居高不下，非洲经济前景依然光明</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/africa-s-economic-outlook-brightens-even-as-price-remains-high</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，非洲的经济前景已经明朗，但面临着从美元复苏到致命干旱等风险，这些风险加剧了非洲已经遭受的“残酷鸡尾酒”冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/africa-s-economic-outlook-brightens-even-as-price-remains-high</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织考虑增加赞比亚资金以帮助应对干旱紧急情况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/imf-considers-upping-zambia-funds-to-help-with-drought-emergency</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织正在与赞比亚进行谈判，以增加对该国的融资，该国正遭受有记录以来最严重的干旱影响，而该国正刚刚摆脱极其缓慢的债务重组进程。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-19/imf-considers-upping-zambia-funds-to-help-with-drought-emergency</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Apr 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
